title: OT: Man Shot Outside AT&T Stadium Following Patriots vs. Cowboys
text: OT: Man Shot Outside AT&T Stadium Following Patriots vs. Cowboys Man Shot Outside AT&T Stadium Following Patriots vs. Cowboys http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2...mming-national According to Ryan Osborne of the Fort Worth Star-Telegram, authorities in Arlington, Texas, have apprehended a male suspect who is believed to have shot a fellow fan outside of AT&T Stadium following Sunday's game between the Dallas Cowboys and New England Patriots.
